{{Infobox CBB Team |name = Rice Owls |logo = RiceOwls.png |logo_size = 160px |university = Rice University |conference = Conference USA |conference_short = C-USA |division = |city = Houston |stateabb = TX |state = Texas |coach = [[Ben Braun]] |tenure = 2nd |arena = [[Tudor Fieldhouse]] |court = Autry Court |capacity = 5,208 |nickname = Owls |studentsection = Autry Army |color1 = Navy |color2 = Gray |fontcolor= white |hex1 = 002469 |hex2 = 5e6062 |h_pattern_b=_thinsidesonwhite|h_body=002469|h_shorts=002469|h_pattern_s=_blanksides2 |a_pattern_b=_thinwhitesides|a_body=002469|a_shorts=002469|a_pattern_s=_whitesides |3_pattern_b=_thinwhitesides|3_body=5e6062|3_shorts=5e6062|3_pattern_s=_whitesides |NCAAchampion = |NCAAfinalfour = |NCAAeliteeight = |NCAAsweetsixteen = 1954 |NCAAsecondround = |NCAAtourneys = 1940, 1942, 1954, 1970 |conference_tournament = |conference_season = Southwest Conference: 1918, 1935, 1940, 1942, 1943, 1944, 1945, 1949, 1954, 1970 }} The '''Rice Owls men's basketball''' program is the [[college basketball|intercollegiate men's basketball]] program of [[Rice University]]. The program is classified in the [[National Collegiate Athletic Association|NCAA]]'s [[Division I (NCAA)|Division I]], and the team competes in [[Conference USA]]. They previously participated in the [[Southwest Conference]] (1914-1996) and the [[Western Athletic Conference]] (1996-2005).
